            <title>小米米家智能水暖毯 1.5m*2m 上架，到手价 449 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/728/319.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/728/319.htm</guid>
